{"sn31.4-12:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 31.4–12 ","sn31.4-12:0.2":"1. Gandhabbavagga ","sn31.4-12:0.3":"Saragandhadidatasuttanavaka ","sn31.4-12:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn31.4-12:1.2":"Ekamantam nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn31.4-12:1.3":"“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena midhekacco kayassa bheda param marana saragandhe adhivatthanam devanam …pe… ","sn31.4-12:1.4":"pheggugandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.5":"tacagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.6":"papatikagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.7":"pattagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.8":"pupphagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.9":"phalagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.10":"rasagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.11":"gandhagandhe adhivatthanam devanam sahabyatam upapajjati”ti? ","sn31.4-12:1.12":"“Idha, bhikkhu, ekacco kayena sucaritam carati, vacaya sucaritam carati, manasa sucaritam carati. ","sn31.4-12:1.13":"Tassa sutam hoti: ","sn31.4-12:1.14":"‘saragandhe adhivattha deva dighayuka vannavanto sukhabahula’ti. ","sn31.4-12:1.15":"Tassa evam hoti: ","sn31.4-12:1.16":"‘aho vataham kayassa bheda param marana saragandhe adhivatthanam devanam …pe… ","sn31.4-12:1.17":"pheggugandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.18":"tacagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.19":"papatikagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.20":"pattagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.21":"pupphagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.22":"phalagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.23":"rasagandhe adhivatthanam devanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.24":"gandhagandhe adhivatthanam devanam sahabyatam upapajjeyyan’ti. ","sn31.4-12:1.25":"So data hoti saragandhanam …pe… ","sn31.4-12:1.26":"so data hoti pheggugandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.27":"so data hoti tacagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.28":"so data hoti papatikagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.29":"so data hoti pattagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.30":"so data hoti pupphagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.31":"so data hoti phalagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.32":"so data hoti rasagandhanam … ","sn31.4-12:1.33":"so data hoti gandhagandhanam. ","sn31.4-12:1.34":"So kayassa bheda param marana gandhagandhe adhivatthanam devanam sahabyatam upapajjati. ","sn31.4-12:1.35":"Ayam kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayam paccayo, yena midhekacco kayassa bheda param marana gandhagandhe adhivatthanam devanam sahabyatam upapajjati”ti. ","sn31.4-12:1.36":"Dvadasamam. "}